Title: Hasratein 2 (Trailer): Akanksha Puri, Puja Banerjee | Gulki, Nyrraa, Dolly, Amika, Saisha
Description:
Hungama OTT presents season 2 of the bold and intimate anthology series – ‘Hasratein’. The series features outstanding actors like Dolly Chawla, Sanam Johar,  Gulki Joshi, Vivek Dahiya, Vinit Kakar, Amika Shail, Saisha Sehgal, Zuber K. Khan, Karan Sharma, Nyrraa M Banerji, Param Singh, Puja Banerjee, Sandeep Kumaar, Akanksha Puri, Rishaab Chauhaan, Navveen Sharrma.
The show traces the stories of six women, each trapped in lives that deny them the love, passion, and tenderness they crave. Behind closed doors and beneath calm exteriors, these women carry secret longings—naughty, intense, rebellious.
From strained marriages to suffocating societal pressures, they each find themselves at a crossroads—ready to break rules, confront fears, and challenge their own beliefs to reclaim their right to feel, to want, and to live fully.
Six women. Six stories. One unshakable desire—to be loved on their own terms, even if it’s just for a few moments.
